{"tid":954664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【孖女三人行】共享男友6年諗住結婚 「阿媽仲想我哋一齊生仔」","createTime":"2018-12-24T18:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T03:57:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35e15162f9e2b5d6440818d464279056b0e30f9a","tid":954664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"常說雙生兒特別心有靈犀，但澳洲有一對孖女不單止外表一樣，連喜歡的男友也一樣！她們亮相電視節目，希望爭取能夠和一起拍拖6年的男友結婚，兩人的母親更希望她們可以一同產子。這對孖女堪稱為世上最相似的一對雙生兒，為了和對方更相似，不惜花了25萬澳元（約138萬港元）整容隆胸。<br />\n來自珀斯的33歲孖女安娜和盧西（Anna and Lucy DeCinque），稱已「分享」同一名男友6年，希望能夠共諧連理。不過根據當地法律，一夫多妻在1961年起已被禁止，所以3人無法結為合法夫婦。於是孖女登上一個電視節目訴苦，希望找到解決辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2LzAwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2LzAwW.png&h=b277f1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲一對孖女希望與同一名男子結婚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90MKXLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90MKXLg.png&h=39345da5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這對孖女（左圖為12歲時照片）豪花25萬澳元整容（右圖）。"},{"pid":"4ead5fc6ee960202cd0add4c2731b6a1a61b8846","tid":954664,"uid":54854,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"12歲個樣靚咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093f181d4953137f3e1081af9a7a0ee78ff7151d","tid":954664,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7a4ccc8f0fcd99342d4107b10525284b26f0e57","tid":954664,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"093f181d4953137f3e1081af9a7a0ee78ff7151d","tid":954664,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"細個幾靚"},{"pid":"0e2425acd1287ae464ac8a3a7942d8087109eb49","tid":954664,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d52f9